# Google Sign-In — same OAuth 2.0 Web client ID as GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID on the server (Google Cloud → Credentials).
# If unset, the app loads the ID from GET /api/auth/config (needs GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID on Netlify for production).
# Restart Vite after editing.
# VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=YOUR_WEB_CLIENT_ID.apps.googleusercontent.com
